high_descs: Go to the table by the door.
Pick up the dirty pot on the table.
Wash the pot in the sink.
Move over to the stove with the clean pot.
Set the clean pot on the back left burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and face the table with the silver bowl.
Pick the pot up from the counter.
Turn around and stand in front of the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink, turn the water on, turn the water off and take the pot out of the sink.
Go right and stand in front of the stove.
Put the pot on the back, left burner.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot on the stove.

high_descs: Walk to the sink, hang a right towards the wall and turn right to face the large table.
Pick up the dirty silver pot in front of the bottle on top of the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink across the room.
Place the dirty pot into the left side of the sink, fill up the sink with water to clean it, and pick up the pot from the sink.
Turn right and walk to the silver stove on your left.
Put the clean pot on the back left burner on top of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot on the stove top.
